{
  "stem": "21319.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I came-- so this woman said to me-- Molly, she says, I'm not going to the camp again.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You can go with the child.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I'm not going.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she went away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was left with my child.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I came over close to that camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- and that the Nazi, the guards shouldn't see me, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I crawled down.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said-- listen, I said, we escaped from a transport and we have nowhere to go.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "How-- that was Vivikond, you know, with the-- can we go with you in the camp?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She says, how will you do it?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They are counting the people, like six people in a row, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I said, we manage.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She says, you know what?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I will give you an old coat I have to hide a baby, you know, and they wouldn't know what it is on the coat, you know.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we waited all day long.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And in the evening, like 6 or 7 o'clock, she give me an old coat, and you know-- and I hide mine child, you know, in the coat, like I was carrying a package.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we went in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We were counting and counting, but they couldn't-- both the fourth or the sixth row, so they didn't pay attention to the last few.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we went in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's how it started in Vivikond.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's what you have here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The next day they were counting, and they didn't know who I am.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't care anymore, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they made me in charge of the children at the-- of the block.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I-- and I saw across from them the big swampy holes where they threw the men every single day and tortured them to death.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The what?",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
